		   README for LTMP (Lighttpd Mysql PHP)

INFOMATION
-------------------------
Why do you recreate the wheel called the LTMP?
Smaller, faster, more efficently.   

What distributions does it support? 
*Only* Debian and Ubuntu supported currently.


INSTALL
------------------------- 
gunzip -cd ltmp.tar.gz | tar xvf -
cd ltmp
./ltmp.sh <domain> <mysql_password for root>


